      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Good staffs and teaching skills are offered",
          "name": "Preethi Helan",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "My engagement with campus life is awsome... Alwys been a part of ncc and cricket matches",
          "name": "Santhosh M",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Teaching methods and all professors are very experienced and good .",
          "name": "Santhosh M",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Placement services need to improve as we do not get many options",
          "name": "Santhosh M",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Staffs are teaching is really good mainly c program, php",
          "name": "P Madhumitha",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The students in the college were very good. They are united among them.",
          "name": "Mohamed Riyas",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "They always keep us in function mood that make us enjoy and study  now they are conducting  many worshops and training  program as well",
          "name": "Kanaga sudali",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Teaching is good. Studied in afternoon batch, so the quality was good.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "the education quality was very good and they mostly focused on academics.",
          "name": "B V Dinesh Kumar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "the canteen is perfect for all the students. very spacious canteen with very tasty food in very affordable price.",
          "name": "vishnu kanth G",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Education not good to the point. Faculties have degree but not quality in teaching",
          "name": "Aadithyan",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Labs to be improved and canteen need to be improved",
          "name": "Santhosh M",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Management should consider some scholarship for poor students",
          "name": "Santhosh M",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The infrastructure facility provided to the students is very bad.",
          "name": "Mohamed Riyas",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is no much support for the sports in the college.",
          "name": "Mohamed Riyas",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "They increased the fees for hostel from 36k to 40k when we questioned theg said they will provide many facilities  but nothing have changed",
          "name": "Kanaga sudali",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Placements was not good. they brought all the non-core companies like Voice, Non-voice process, Bank trainee etc. all the non core companies only except one or two",
