          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "there will be no events frequently and less interaction",
          "name": "B V Dinesh Kumar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "lack of amenities like wifi and air conditioner",
          "name": "vishnu kanth G",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Food is not that good in canteen and the rate is quite high than the quality",
